articles.author: Nidhi Verma, Dmitry Zhdannikov
articles.title: US to impose sanctions on Russian oil fleet and traders, document shows - Reuters
articles.description: The United States will impose some of the harshest sanctions yet on Russia's oil industry, according to a purported U.S. Treasury document circulating among traders in Europe and Asia that drove global oil prices 3% higher on Friday.
